    <note>Ma(2) Zhijie [8103] His grandson, Qingchong (not in dataset), came to Wang Anshi and requested a funerary inscription for the first time in 1062. Zhejie's ancestors were Fufeng Ma(2). His 6th generation unnamed ancestor, A [3661], moved to Yuzhou, Jixian. His father, Quanyi [3663], who assisted Taizu in pacifying the empire, moved to Kaifeng after Yuzhou fell to the Khitan. Wang Anshi, WJ, 87.906-909. CBD, 3, 1843.</note>
